data.description: Cute Brick Home in the Heart of Titusville, minutes away from the Historic Downtown Titusville. Enjoy a beautifully done split floorplan, newer flooring throughout the house, a newer roof, newer air-conditioning system, newer hot water heater, newer ceiling fans, fixtures and security system. Home was remodeled in 2020 with new cabinets, granite countertops and new stainless appliances. Updated bathrooms have new vanities, mirrors, lighting fixtures & toilets. Home interior/exterior has been painted as well!
